{
  "stem": "2004.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was giving sort of punishment, trying to save people's lives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it wasn't-- the reputations that were outside the camp were really not always true.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In some cases, these people were rough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they tried to save somebody's life by giving them a few-- a few whacks, but they could really survive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in that camp of Pustkow, we were doing various jobs-- shoe repairs, clothing repairs, things like this just to keep us busy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One day, while being in Pustkow-- and we are now in the winter months of 1943.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It must've been December or thereabouts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A group of German SS came to the camp and made an announcement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They are looking for volunteers [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] for a special work detail.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They need young men who are able to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the job is probably no more than for a week or thereabouts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they will be very well-rewarded with ample food, extra rations, special clothing, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they assembled us all in the assembly. in the-- there was like-- they used to call it the appel-platz, which means where you gather every morning and you have a headcount.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gathered us there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, well, whoever wants to, we are looking for-- I think, it was somewhere around 30 or 35 people out of, maybe, 200 or so, 250.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whoever wants those special rations and doesn't mind working for a week, please step aside to the left or wherever it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, being young-- and extra rations, extra clothing, this sounded like paradise to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I stepped aside and decided, why not?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, look, I've been working anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Might as well work for extra rations.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
